# Install instructions

Put both `php_redis_*.dll` and `php_igbinary_*.dll` in your php extensions folder and add both to `php.ini`.

# Compile flags

`--enable-redis=shared`
`--enable-redis-session`
`--enable-igbinary=shared`
`--enable-redis-igbinary`
